On echo RPi, set server ip in /etc/config/cgminer:
    uci set cgminer.default.server=192.168.1.3
    uci commit
And upload cgminer-monitor to /usr/bin/cgminer-monitor,
 cgminer.init to /etc/init.d/cgminer

On server, install rsyslog, edit /etc/rsyslogd.conf:
    
    #################
    #### MODULES ####
    #################

    ...
    ...
    ...

    # provides UDP syslog reception
    #$ModLoad imudp
    #$UDPServerRun 514

    # provides TCP syslog reception
    $ModLoad imtcp
    $InputTCPServerRun 514

    ...
    ...
    ...

    ###############
    #### RULES ####
    ###############
    if $fromhost-ip startswith '192.168.1.' then /var/log/rpi.log
    & ~

    ...
    ...
    ...

Change ip setting (192.168.1.3 and 192.168.1.) according to your network.
